Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:02.40,italics,,0,0,0,,Satou-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:09.50,italics,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s fed up with playing your games!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:13.32,italics,,0,0,0,,In short, the plan is to release the recovered \Nnerve gas underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:15.63,italics,,0,0,0,, and render Satou powerless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:20.72,italics,,0,0,0,,In order to avoid alerting Satou, \Nwe can’t evacuate the citizens.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:24.94,italics,,0,0,0,,About four hours remain.\NBefore then, we have to capture Satou at any cost!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.19,italics,,0,0,0,,Go, ghost!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.71,italics,,0,0,0,,Fight to the death to stop him!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:29.78,italics,,0,0,0,,I know that!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:33.84,italics,,0,0,0,,He’s not a revolutionary or a tactician.\NHe’s just a player.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.68,italics,,0,0,0,,And that’s exactly why we have room \Nto take advantage of him. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.27,italics,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:40.04,italics,,0,0,0,,Bury him alive.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.71,italics,,0,0,0,,You put some thought into it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:47.96,italics,,0,0,0,,But... just when you thought you'd won...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:51.61,italics,,0,0,0,,The rug gets pulled out from under you!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.21,italics,,0,0,0,,W- What’s going on?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:54.67,italics,,0,0,0,,Are they digging in?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.71,italics,,0,0,0,,We overdid it!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.12,italics,,0,0,0,,No, the floor-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.19,italics,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:11.08,italics,,0,0,0,,I’ll kill... every last one of you-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.75,italics,,0,0,0,,We couldn’t defeat him?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:19.66,italics,,0,0,0,,Game... start!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai! Nagai!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Search team!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At point F2, there’s been an explosion\N and a large-scale collapse.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like below the underground tunnel, \Nthere's an even older passage.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t reach Okuyama and the others.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Naga-\NNakano, shut up!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.56,upper,,0,0,0,,Nagai!\N Where’s Satou-san?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.17,upper,,0,0,0,,He’s not here.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.45,upper,,0,0,0,,Neither are Izumi-san and the others!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:41.60,upper,,0,0,0,,That way’s blocked off!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.26,upper,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.20,upper,,0,0,0,,No idea!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.04,upper,,0,0,0,,But it looks like we were done in. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.51,upper,,0,0,0,,That we were the ones buried?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.02,upper,,0,0,0,,...Which means, the problem is Satou-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.02,upper,,0,0,0,,If he’s not defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he’ll come after us while we’re not paying attention. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Satou?\NProbably!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the ones he’s fighting are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosa- \NIzumi-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan. Please!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the type who keeps my things in \Ngood working order.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from earlier!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s no good.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the damage to the unit?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No damage! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a trap. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will there be a problem with releasing the gas?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The conditions have changed slightly, but \Nthey’re all within our expectations.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when the installation has been \Ncompleted, withdraw immediately.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll also withdraw in five minutes. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m burdening you like this.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don’t worry about it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my job-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re first up.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun. Can you hear me?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make you regret getting\N in my way so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,, you'll wish you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One down. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re supposed to be human!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m a ghost.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At Musashi Heavy Industries...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have died.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Three people confirmed!\NThey’re ajin!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them all in!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids go on ahead!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Tosaki-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The bank. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In that safe-deposit box is the proof \Nthat you’re an ajin. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet and listen.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The key for the safe-deposit box \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is in her hospital room.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand, then go.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With this leg, \Nthere's no way for me to escape.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But, surely Nagai-kun and-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I release you from your contract.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and disappear.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I’m...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...free?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Live as you like.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... \NI’m free to protect you, Tosaki-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiotic-\NI won’t take orders anymore. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was released from my contract.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... for the new life.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!\NYou can’t beat him!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you’re number two. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't manage...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll let you meet your new self!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It’s Nagai.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your game is over, Satou-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a bit late?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Excuse me. \N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I went the wrong direction. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.84,upper,,0,0,0,,Commander. This way.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.48,upper,,0,0,0,,How’s the installation?  \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.55,upper,,0,0,0,,Complete. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:58.80,upper,,0,0,0,,Excellent.  \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.20,upper,,0,0,0,,Wait for orders.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:04.94,upper,,0,0,0,,Shit!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.89,upper,,0,0,0,,This is payback for earlier!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:17.72,upper,,0,0,0,,You-!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:20.86,upper,,0,0,0,,Damn-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.33,upper,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.51,upper,,0,0,0,,I’m always taking care of you. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I’ll make sure you thank me. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tanaka-kun!  \N I’ll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s one thing I want to ask you, Nagai-kun. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get in my way?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it obvious?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll never be able to live a quiet life!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re the same as me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d rather you not lump me together \Nwith a lunatic like yourself.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s do this, ghost!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the same.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to live quietly.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play to the very bottom of my heart. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But this world won’t allow that!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,ghost!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why we’re doing what we\N should to each other!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you would, Nagai-kun.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As foolish as always.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s the result of experience in\N battle, I suppose. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You get what you deserve.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Izumi-san...  go....\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make you pay for that time at the hospital!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let Izumi-san... go...\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You too?\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t get in my way!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than five minutes remain.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the key lock.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander! It’s Satou!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve got Satou!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The orders were to...\Nuse the most surefire method to capture Satou!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember my promise\N at the research lab, Nagai-kun?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I would cut off your head.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I’ll fulfill that promise.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll pick up your severed head, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and make you watch as a new head is created.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You will watch until you die.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You will no longer be yourself. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I’ll show the new you \Nthe best show you’ve ever seen.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,First...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eriko-chan!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Kaito-kun and your parents.	\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then... Tosaki-kun.\NShimomura-san, Nakano-kun....\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them,\N I’ll kill them in front of your eyes.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like at Musashi Heavy Industries.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your punishment for getting in my way.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I make promises too, Satou-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever you go...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find you and kill you!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai!! Nagai-kun!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, nothing good comes from saving people.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We’ll act as your pawns!\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won’t do it.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry up and die.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shut up. \N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It’s your fault my quiet life is all messed up.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m sorry to have caused you trouble. \N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was sick... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that’s just what happens.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to take a piss.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should be the one saying that\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As your immortal soldiers!\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The flood phenomenon.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Send out the IBM-\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can wait as long as you want, \Nbut the U.S. forces aren’t coming!\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only bothered with him because\N he seemed pitiful and alone.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagai-kun.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t move!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,, I’m-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take him!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ajin are under the protection\N of the Japanese government. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And that woman is a human, working under me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou and Tanaka.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already reached an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the American side gave up the plan of \Nusing the gas just before it was time. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m grateful, Senpai.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for stopping Satou,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,all of you will be pardoned, and free to go.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your persistence with \Nyour idiotic arrangements. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t forget to erase my \Nresponsibility for my crimes. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:20.28,upper,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This afternoon, within the government, the cabinet made \Na new decision regarding measures concerning ajin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:29.18,upper,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After much deliberation, the National Diet has approved \Na new bill making civil rights a reality for ajin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With the enactment of this measure-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for a blood sample.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,, Did you see your brother again?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice that you get along. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not like we get along that well. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why he wanted to go out with me!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, that’s something!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that pretty awful?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s really funny.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been a while, hasn’t it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry, hurry, hurry!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe they really exist.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NI didn’t believe it until now.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re humans that don’t die. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how the hell they get that way. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it’s almost like a game.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It’d be so much fun to have a body like that.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I had a dream for the first\N time in a long time. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe you can sleep\N in a situation like this. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we don’t know \Nwhat will happen to us now.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously we’ll start our second playthrough.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we going to do that?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it when a plan comes together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-kun. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after the U.S. forces took him into custody.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept that fact quiet.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the details when you get here. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll pick you up shortly.\N
